  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Improving Adolescent Nutrition Outcomes</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The aim of the project is to improve nutrition outcomes for adolescents (10-19yrs) and their children (0-5yrs). The project will target the adolescent through their lifecycle focusing on the periods before, during and after pregnancy.  The project will use a resilience approach that promotes partnership, integration and empowerment.</narrative>
  </description>
  <description type="2">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The change the project will achieve is improve the nutrition outcomes of adolescence girls and their children through improved nutrition practices and access to quality nutrition services and information</narrative>
  </description>
